data.label: Dropbox Core SDK for Java
data.description: 一个 Java 库，用于访问 Dropbox 的基于 HTTP 的核心 API v2。此 SDK 还支持较旧的核心 API v1，但该支持将在某个时候被删除。

data.label: Dropbox Core SDK for Java
data.description: A Java library to access Dropbox's HTTP-based Core API v2. This SDK also supports the older Core API v1, but that support will be removed at some point.
